				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: The Only Reason I Play EverQuest --&gt; Bard :)<a name="53011"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 21 04 11:26 AM</span></td>
